.SH NAME
w3m \- a text based Web browser and pager
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B w3m
[options] [URL or filename]
.PP
Use "w3m -h" to display a complete list of current options.
.SH DESCRIPTION
.\" This defines appropriate quote strings for nroff and troff
